eiteam.esteemedinnovation.api.exosuit

Class ExosuitEventDelegator

  • java.lang.Object
    • eiteam.esteemedinnovation.api.exosuit.ExosuitEventDelegator

  • public class ExosuitEventDelegator
extends java.lang.Object
    Do not register this class to the event bus, or you will cause the ExosuitUpgrade methods to get called multiple times (bad). This is registered in the static initializer for ExosuitRegistry.

      • doMethodForEachUpgrade

        private static void doMethodForEachUpgrade(net.minecraft.entity.player.EntityPlayer player,
                                           TriConsumer<ExosuitEventHandler,net.minecraft.item.ItemStack,net.minecraft.inventory.EntityEquipmentSlot> func)
        Iterates over each armor slot, gets the exosuit armor in that slot, and calls the provided function for every installed ExosuitEventHandler.
        Parameters:
        player - The player whose armor to iterate through.
        func - A void function that passes the current ExosuitEventHandler, the armor ItemStack, and EntityEquipmentSlot containing this armor.
